#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/getting_started/first_campaign.rst-1
msgid ""
"How the filter rule equation fields look in Odoo Marketing Automation "
"campaigns."
msgstr "筛选规则等式字段在 Odoo 营销自动化活动中的外观。"

